Senior Multichannel Marketing Manager
29 Apr 2014 06:09 PM - UAE
. About UsWe're hiring!There has never been a better time to join Provident Financial Group. Wehave a strong and clear agenda this year that will transform our business intoa truly multichannel organisation. We have already launched a successful new product – Satsuma – andwe are looking to launch another new product this year! This will enable us tocontinue to grow our business from the strong position we are already in,increasing our share in the UK non-standard credit market.So, if you have aspirations to join a forward thinking and innovative organisation, Provident Financial Group could be theplace for you! About the RoleA rare and exciting opportunity has arisen for an experienced and highlymotivated individual to join our Home Credit Marketing team. As a Senior MultichannelMarketing Manager you will be responsible for developing and executingour Home Credit Marketing plan. The successful candidate will exceed customeracquisition, engagement and retention targets while effectively leading anddeveloping the Home Credit Marketing team.Develop digital and offline capabilities across all forms of media Develop the Home Credit brandDrive winning Advertising campaigns across all media to exceed customeracquisition targetsDevelop and execute retention targetsDevelop and manage online/offline customer experienceSupport, coach, motivate and mentor the Home Credit Marketing team About YouThe successful candidate will have experience of;Online, offline and direct mail marketingManaging and building brands and running campaignsTeam ManagementAgency ManagementBuilding relationships with key stakeholders across the businessDefining and embedding a customer journey  Sound like you?Customer driven and committed to delivering exceptional customerexperiences Proactive and enthusiasticResilient and have the ability to deliver under pressureStrong organisational skillsGood negotiating skillsIf the above sounds like you then please don't hesitate to apply today! We look forward to receiving your application.
